    bestScenario: "A winter evening where the Golden Retriever comes home buzzing from a social event and the Cozy Blanket has the fire going. The Golden Retriever talks. The Cozy Blanket listens. The warmth is mutual but different — active and passive, giving and receiving, both exactly what the other needs.",
    worstScenario: "A year where neither voices a concern and the sediment builds until the distance feels permanent. The Golden Retriever is still warm but the warmth is performative. The Cozy Blanket is still present but the presence is hollow. Both are technically fine and fundamentally lonely.",
