    worstScenario: "An event where the Disco Ball gets all the credit and the Swiss Army Knife, who made it possible, is invisible. The Swiss Army Knife says nothing. The resentment builds silently. By the next event, the Swiss Army Knife has withdrawn their support, and the Disco Ball cannot understand why the lights suddenly do not work.",
